headline: EYLEA HD速 (aflibercept) Injection 8 mg Applications for Expanded U.S. Label and Prefilled Syringe Receive FDA Review Period Extension
summary: TARRYTOWN, N.Y., Aug. 20, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Regeneron Pharmaceuticals, Inc. (NASDAQ: REGN) today announced that the U.S. Food and Drug Administration (FDA) has extended the target action dates to the fourth quarter of 2025 for two EYLEA HD速 (aflibercept) Injection 8 mg regulatory submissions. This includes a Chemistry, Manufacturing and Controls (CMC) Prior-Approval Supplement (PAS) for the EYLEA HD prefilled syringe and a supplemental Biologics License Application (sBLA) seeking approval
